1 1. Position No. 1: The term of office of one member shall
2 expire on the 30th day of June, 2000, and each seven (7) years
3 thereafter;
4 2. Position No. 2: The term of office of one member shall
5 expire on the 30th day of June, 2001, and each seven (7) years
6 thereafter;
7 3. Position No. 3: The term of office of one member shall
8 expire on the 30th day of June, 2002, and each seven (7) years
9 thereafter;
10 4. Position No. 4: The term of office of one member shall
11 expire on the 30th day of June, 2003, and each seven (7) years
12 thereafter;
13 5. Position No. 5: The term of office of one member shall
14 expire on the 30th day of June, 2004, and each seven (7) years
15 thereafter;
16 6. Position No. 6: The term of office of one member shall
17 expire on the 30th day of June, 2005, and each seven (7) years
18 thereafter;
19 7. Position No. 7: The term of office of one member shall
20 expire on the 30th day of June, 2006, and each seven (7) years
21 thereafter;
22 8. Position No. 8: The term of office shall coincide with the
23 member's term on the A&M Board; and
24
